OL,3,CMeet the graduate retraining as a
OL,4,Cplumber to beat AI
OL,6,FA female psychology graduate is
OL,7,Fretraining as a plumber in an attempt
OL,8,Fto pursue a career that AI can't take
OL,9,Fover.
OL,11,FHeena Kerai, 21, completed her degree
OL,12,Fat Edge Hill University, in Ormskirk,
OL,13,Fat the cost of #30,000, but turned her
OL,14,Fback on the career after noticing the
OL,15,Frapid advance of AI.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
