CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781712674
OL,3,CMeet the graduate retraining as a
OL,4,Cplumber to beat AI
OL,6,F"Seeing that AI is taking over so many
OL,7,Fjobs, why not pursue that interest
OL,8,F(plumbing) and take it further,
OL,9,Fbecause I know its a job that AI cant
OL,10,Fdo, not while I'm alive anyway," Heena
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FHeena, from Bolton, started looking
OL,14,Finto plumbing courses during her
OL,15,Fsecond year. While training, she is
OL,16,Fworking part time as a Special
OL,17,FEducational Needs teaching assistant
OL,18,Fto begin paying off her university
OL,19,Fdebt.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
