OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781712674
OL,3,CMeet the graduate retraining as a
OL,4,Cplumber to beat AI
OL,6,FShe is currently two years into her
OL,7,Fthree and a half year course and is
OL,8,Fdocumenting her journey on social
OL,9,Fmedia.
OL,11,FHer interest in plumbing comes from
OL,12,Fher father Vilash Kerai who also works
OL,13,Fin the trade.
OL,15,FShe said: "When your parents are doing
OL,16,Fwork around the house, you don't tend
OL,17,Fto get involved but I would get
OL,18,Finvovled. My dad would tell me, come
OL,19,Fhere and watch what I'm doing, its a
OL,20,Flife skill."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
