OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1781712674
OL,3,CMeet the graduate retraining as a
OL,4,Cplumber to beat AI
OL,6,FFigures from the Office of National
OL,7,FStatistics show that as of 2025 there
OL,8,Fwere only 3,028 female plumbers in the
OL,9,FUK - compared to 146,280 men in the
OL,10,Findustry.
OL,12,FAlthough the trade is still not as
OL,13,Fpopular among women, Heena's teacher
OL,14,Fsays more companies are looking for
OL,15,Fwomen tradies: "A lot of companies now
OL,16,Fare facing a lot of challenges with
OL,17,Fvulnerable customers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
